Summary: UFO or IFO ?, it shows up on my rainbows pictures
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was Wednesday 23 7:00 AM and with a light rain, a beautiful double raibow formed North to West in the sky, I run inside and I took some pictures with my 7 megapixel point and shoot FinePix S5700 digital camera. That night went I arrived home from work and was looking at the pictures in the computer, I notice 2 dots, the closer one looks strange when I zoomed in with the mouse (egg shaped with a long shadow bellow), the blurry corner on the botton right of the picture is a rain drop on the protective filter.
